<item>
            <title>[TEZ-134] Untangle MR configuration in YarnTezDagChild</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/TEZ-134</link>
                <project id="12314426" key="TEZ">Apache Tez</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;MR configuration is set in several different places in YarnTezDagChild (and MRTask), some of which is used during task initialization, other after. This makes the runtime brittle, and changing it tedious. If possible, we should simplify individual task setup - and differentiate between Tez and MR configuration.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
