                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="13661482" author="sseth" created="Sun, 19 May 2013 03:50:46 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch makes the following changes&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Removes all MR references from YARNTezDAGChild.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Introduces a new Task - MRRuntimeTask, which is responsible for all the MR initialization&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Couple of new Tez config parameters&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Fixes config parameters which are meant to point to a list of directories versus a single job directory.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Passes all unit tests, and tested on a local cluster. Will commit this in a bit.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
